Think2Create

Modules and UserRoles:
1. Business Requirement Generation (Business User)
2. Requirement Breakdown (Business Analyst)
3. Documentation Generation (Developer or Analyst)

Module 1: Business Requirement Generation (Business User)
Input: Natural language prompt describing the business problem.
Output: Structured Business Requirement Document (BRD).

Module 2. Requirement Breakdown (Business Analyst)
Input: BRD
Output: Epics, user stories, sub-tasks (Jira-compatible format).

Module 3. Documentation Generation (Developer or Analyst)
Inputs: BRD
Outputs:
Solution Design Document (SDD) or
Process Design Document (PDD) or
Developer Notes / Tech Specs or
Helping in understanding the requirements

TechStack:
Ollama
Custom Seperate model creating using ModelFile
hungging face - transformers
python
